title: Episode 362: Internally Excited (Feat. Brent Faiyaz)
itunes:title: Episode 362: Internally Excited (Feat. Brent Faiyaz)
description:
R&B Singer, Brent Faiyaz joins the ladies of Lip Service this week to promote his latest album 'Wasteland.' Brent, who's a typically introverted, opens up about being labeled toxic, falling in and out love quickly, his mom still talking to his ex's, and much more. Enjoy!
